      ],
      "title": null,
      "content": "在 Meta 被小扎开除之后的杨乐坤（Yann LeCun）创办了一个新的公司 AMI Labs。 拿到了现在应该是最多钱的种子轮，共计 10.3 亿美元。 他看不上大语言模型这一套，所以他的目标是创建一个能够真正理解现实世界、能够长期记忆并进行规划的智能系统。 走的路线的话，应该就是他之前一直说的要做“世界模型”。 产品应该是机器人、工业控制、复杂自动化、可穿戴设备等等，旨在现实世界构建一层可以计算的、物理加常识的基础设施。 他一直认为：真正的智能并非始于语言，而是始于世界，观点主要是： 1. LLM 压缩过语言的并不能代表世界本身 2. 纯 generative 的自监督预测，不适合所有现实数据。 3. 世界模型的目标，是支持 Agent 能做长期规划和安全的进行控制 AMI Labs (@amilabs) Advanced Machine Intelligence (AMI) is building a new breed of AI systems that understand the world, have persistent memory, can reason and plan, and are controllable and safe. We’ve raised a $1.03B (~€890M) round from global investors who believe in our vision of universally intelligent systems centered on world models. This round is co-led by Cathay Innovation, Greycroft, Hiro Capital, HV Capital, and Bezos Expeditions, along with other investors and angels across the world. We are a growing team of researchers and builders, operating in Paris, New York, Montreal and Singapore from day one. Read more: amilabs.xyz/ AMI - Real world. Real intelligence. — https://nitter.net/amilabs/status/2031234832454324639#m",
      "url": "https://x.com/op7418/status/2032016233172992083",
      "images": null,
      "published": "2026-03-12T08:49:57+00:00",
      "hasTranscript": false
    },
